Class ELImgTag

java.lang.Object
jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport

org.apache.struts.taglib.html.ImgTag
org.apache.strutsel.taglib.html.ELImgTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
BodyTag, IterationTag, JspTag, Tag, Serializable
public class ELImgTag extends ImgTag

Generate an IMG tag to the specified image URI.

TODO:

  • make the alt and src settable from properties (for i18n)
  • handle onLoad, onAbort, and onError events (my JavaScript book is very old, there may be more unsupported events in the past couple of IE versions)

This class is a subclass of the class org.apache.struts.taglib.html.ImgTag which provides most of the described functionality. This subclass allows all attribute values to be specified as expressions utilizing the JavaServer Pages Standard Library expression language.
